1
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,520
What's going on?

2
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:30,280
Look.

3
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:40,840
What exactly is this situation?

4
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,440
Is it someone's prank?

5
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:50,740
This...

6
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,280
What is this?

7
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,729
An illusion?

8
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:55,880
Wait.

9
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:04,180
Clan Elder,

10
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:05,850
I have something to report.

11
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:08,520
What is the meaning of this behavior?

12
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:11,240
Today, our Hu family

13
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:12,840
is about to hold

14
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:15,700
the succession ceremony for the head of the family.

15
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:16,840
You barging in like this,

16
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:19,280
shouting and yelling,

17
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:21,280
wouldn't it make outsiders

18
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,920
laugh at our Hu family?

19
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:25,079
We can discuss everything tomorrow.

20
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:25,740
Clan Elder.

21
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,680
This is a matter of great importance.

22
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:28,340
We cannot delay even for a day.

23
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,320
Hu Wenzhong and his family

24
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:31,760
for many years

25
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,800
have deliberately

26
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,329
deceived our clan members.

27
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,000
If I wait one more day,

28
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,530
the entire Hu family

29
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,920
will be deceived for another day.

30
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:40,480
I...

31
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:41,720
I really

32
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,120
cannot feel at peace.

33
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,440
Hu Wenyi,

34
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,160
do you know

35
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:47,960
the weight of those words?

36
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,680
Tell us,

37
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,360
how did the mother and son

38
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,480
deceive our clan members?

39
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:57,540
Clan Elder,

40
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:58,840
everyone.

41
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,640
Standing before you

42
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:01,640
is

43
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,440
the daughter of Hu Wenzhong,

44
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,440
Hu Linglong.

45
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:10,050
Brother was pushed into the water.

46
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,920
Hahaha.

47
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:14,840
Absurd!

48
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:16,810
The Hu family...

49
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,079
Which clan member

50
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,130
doesn't know

51
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:22,360
that Hu Linglong, over a decade ago,

52
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,480
drowned and died young?

53
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,200
How is that possible?

54
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,540
Clan Elder.

55
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:30,520
This is the scheme of Hu Wenzhong's family.

56
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:31,960
After Hu Qingyun died,

57
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,880
Hu Linglong has been dressing as a man

58
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,040
in front of the clan members for years,

59
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:36,120
pretending to be the young master.

60
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:36,760
Now,

61
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,520
she even wants to make it real

62
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,520
and inherit our Hu family's estate.

63
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:41,000
Hmph!

64
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,040
Letting our Hu family

65
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:43,800
fall into the hands of

66
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,680
a lowly and contemptible woman.

67
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:46,840
Hu Wenyi,

68
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,400
you have no proof,

69
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,840
stop talking nonsense here.

70
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,000
No proof?

71
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,440
If we had no proof,

72
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:54,800
how would we dare speak nonsense before the Clan Elder?

73
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,480
You two,

74
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,400
do you remember this person?

75
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,800
Doctor Xue.

76
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,680
You are?

77
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,240
Replying to the Clan Elder,

78
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:06,700
I am a doctor from Jishi Hall in Qimen County.

79
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,120
Today, I come

80
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,720
at the request of Master Hu Wenyi

81
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:10,920
to bear witness.

82
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,360
Go ahead and speak.

83
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:16,640
Hu Qingyun,

84
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:19,000
she is indeed a woman.

85
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:20,760
What should we do?

86
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:22,840
It was twenty years ago,

87
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:24,240
on the 9th day of the 10th month.

88
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,320
That day, Hu Wenzhong

89
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,880
suddenly carried a drowning Hu Qingyun

90
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:28,560
to seek my help.

91
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,320
Unfortunately, it was too late.

92
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:32,840
At that time, Hu Qingyun had already stopped breathing,

93
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:34,640
and there was nothing I could do.

94
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,000
Entrusted by him,

95
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:39,040
I have kept this matter a secret

96
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:41,280
and never revealed a word to anyone.

97
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,560
Doctor,

98
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,960
how is my son's injury?

99
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,600
Please don't worry, Madam,

100
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,320
the young master is fine.

101
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,440
Doctor,

102
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,520
why haven't I seen Dr. Xue today?

103
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,860
Haven't you heard?

104
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:54,480
He went to the Hu family ancestral hall with Hu Wenyi,

105
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,240
supposedly to serve as a witness

106
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,800
to prove that the Hu family's young master, Hu Qingyun,

107
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,000
is actually a woman.

108
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:01,960
Zhinian,

109
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:02,760
where are you going?

110
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:03,560
Young Master.

111
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,290
Are you sure?

112
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,440
I'm sure.

113
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:17,680
Elder,

114
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,040
say no more.

115
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:21,960
Now,

116
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,840
I would like to hear

117
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:25,370
what Hu Linglong has to say.

118
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:26,560
No.

119
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,720
No, Elder,

120
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:28,840
he is talking nonsense.

121
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,600
He is lying!

122
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,159
I

123
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:34,760
am willing to guarantee with my reputation from years of practicing medicine

124
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,280
that every word I said is true,

125
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:37,680
without any falsehood.

126
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:38,960
It's not true.

127
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,120
They are lying.

128
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:44,240
Are you saying

129
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,120
what they said isn't true?

130
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,180
Then let me ask you:

131
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:49,360
Why,

132
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:51,940
why is the name on your father,

133
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,680
Hu Wenzhong's suicide note,

134
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,680
not Hu Qingyun,

135
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,480
but your real name, Hu Linglong?

136
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,120
Didn't you want me

137
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,600
to be Hu Qingyun for the rest of my life?

138
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,320
Why in the suicide note

139
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:02,080
did you write my real name?

140
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,360
Dr. Xue.

141
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:07,360
My husband treated you well when he was alive.

142
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,720
Now that he has just passed away,

143
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,120
you...

144
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,080
how could you do

145
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,640
such a treacherous thing?

146
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,080
Madam,

147
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,800
you can't blame me.

148
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,880
My family has faced disasters recently,

149
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:19,160
and it was Master Hu Wenyi who helped us.

150
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:21,160
I'm just returning the favor.

151
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,480
Since I have already testified,

152
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,760
the rest is your

153
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:26,320
Hu family's private matter.

154
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:26,800
I...

155
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,580
I will take my leave first.

156
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,400
Farewell.

157
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,440
I'm sorry.

158
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:30,920
Sigh.

159
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,200
Go.

160
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,159
Farewell, Master Hu.

161
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:35,920
Go.

162
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,250
Clan elders.

163
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,320
Everyone knows that our Hu family tea

164
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,560
is the best in Qimen.

165
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:47,360
Everyone knows that our Hu clan

166
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,890
is wealthy and prosperous.

167
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,180
Hu Wenzhong's family,

168
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,520
out of selfish desires,

169
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,840
wants to monopolize the family business.

170
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:55,680
That's why they came up with this trick

171
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,720
of a woman dressing as a man.

172
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,600
Yes.

173
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,040
My father is right.

174
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:04,680
Everyone.

175
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,320
If you are unwilling to believe

176
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,840
our one-sided story,

177
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:08,960
you can just take her

178
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,400
to another doctor.

179
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:11,600
Have him check her pulse and body,

180
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,330
and the truth will be revealed.

181
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,660
Somebody come!

182
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,120
Take her away.

183
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,640
Yes.

184
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,440
Take her away.

185
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,600
Let go.

186
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,560
Don't grab her.

187
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,440
Don't touch me.

188
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,240
What are you all doing?

189
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:23,880
Don't touch me.

190
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:24,640
Let go.

191
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,530
Give it to me.

192
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:26,680
Give it to me!

193
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,280
Let go.

194
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:36,480
Linglong.

195
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,680
Linglong.

196
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,080
Daughter, what's wrong?

197
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,360
Wake up.

198
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,280
My child.

199
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:48,720
Linglong.

200
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,320
Linglong.

201
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:53,120
Wake up.

202
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,000
So many of you

203
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,409
bullying a widow and her child.

204
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:59,380
What are you doing?

205
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:00,280
Hey!

206
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:00,920
Hey!

207
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:03,520
Linglong.

208
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,720
Linglong.

209
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,040
No!

210
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,320
Where...

211
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,520
Where am I?

212
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:25,130
How did I end up in a place like this?

213
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,360
Who is in my body?

214
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,240
Why does it look different again?

215
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,240
These clothes...

216
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,200
This hair...

217
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:32,520
Did I time-travel?

218
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:33,960
What dynasty is this?

219
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,360
Why did I turn into a man?

220
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:38,080
How was my body taken away?

221
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:38,720
No.

222
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,169
I need to get out of here.

223
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:41,360
Ah!

224
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,800
Who exactly are you?

225
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:47,120
Why are you in my body?

226
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:50,840
Could it be that I've been hit by

227
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:53,120
the legendary body-snatching spell?

228
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,480
What should I do?

229
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,880
Wretched girl!

230
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:59,200
How dare you disguise yourself as a man to steal my position as head of the family.

231
00:08:59,200 --> 00:08:59,880
Today,

232
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:01,600
I'll tear off your mask.

233
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:02,960
Ah.

234
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:04,440
Father.

235
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:10,880
Hey.

236
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:12,040
You must never admit it.

237
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:13,240
Do you hear me?

238
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,680
Where is this?

239
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:15,920
Just now,

240
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:17,400
it was the jade pendant speaking.

241
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:18,260
Somebody come!

242
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,880
Strip off her clothes

243
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,080
and pull her hair!

244
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,330
Let everyone see

245
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,880
if she is a good man,

246
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,120
or a shameless,

247
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:25,840
deceitful

248
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,760
wench!

249
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:27,280
No!

250
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:27,840
Stop!

251
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:34,960
Let's see who dares to touch her.

252
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,000
Zhinian.

253
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:39,640
Why is he back?

254
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,200
Remember,

255
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,450
the one who drowned that day

256
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,260
was the Hu family's daughter,

257
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,120
Hu Linglong.

258
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,360
The one alive today

259
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,600
is the Hu family's eldest son,

260
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,440
Hu Qingyun.

261
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,320
Linglong,

262
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,970
for your father and mother,

263
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:03,960
and for the Hu family,

264
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,760
you must live on behalf of your brother.

265
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,800
Why do you wear boys' clothes?

266
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:13,280
You are obviously a girl.

267
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,480
Father told me to do so.

268
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:18,080
He said I must live on behalf of my brother.

269
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,890
You must never tell anyone.

270
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,120
Wait for me.

271
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:30,240
These are all the memories of the original owner of this body.

272
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,120
No.

273
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,440
Xu Zhinian.

274
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:33,840
Humph.

275
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:36,240
This is a family matter of the Hu family.

276
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:38,080
You're just a wet-behind-the-ears brat.

277
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,680
What right do you have to interfere?

278
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:41,440
I don't care about the Hu family's affairs.

279
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:43,100
But if you try to hurt Qingyun,

280
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,720
I won't just stand by.

281
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:45,640
Humph.

282
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,200
Qingyun.

283
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:48,680
Humph.

284
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:51,840
Hu Qingyun has been dead for a long time.

285
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:52,920
Did you know

286
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:53,840
that your own brother

287
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:55,120
is actually a woman?

288
00:10:58,960 --> 00:10:59,800
Zhinian.

289
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,640
Great.

290
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:07,000
So you knew all along.

291
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,400
Ah.

292
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,240
Hu Linglong.

293
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:11,700
You have deceived the Hu family in every way,

294
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,880
yet you confided in an outsider.

295
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:17,250
You really don't know who your true family is.

296
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,400
In my opinion,

297
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,160
she and Xu Zhinian

298
00:11:21,160 --> 00:11:22,690
have been having an affair.

299
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:25,120
All she thinks about is romance.

300
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,200
If she were really made the head of the family,

301
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:30,860
the Hu family would be handed over to outsiders.

302
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,120
Such a person

303
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:32,960
is truly

304
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:34,440
shameless.

305
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,640
Full of feudal dregs.

306
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:37,600
No wonder they say women are trouble.

307
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,480
I really need to sort out this Hu family.

308
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,210
Despicable.

309
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:41,640
Exactly.

310
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:43,640
Women are lowly.

311
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,840
Then weren't you also born of a lowly person?

312
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,840
What does that make you?

313
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:48,520
A bastard.

314
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:49,240
A coward.

315
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,280
See that?

316
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:51,000
Ah.

317
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:53,240
This is outrageous.

318
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:54,890
You curse me?

319
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,560
Even if I am truly a woman,

320
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:57,440
so what?

321
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,000
Father.

322
00:11:59,200 --> 00:11:59,640
This...

323
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:02,120
Then you don't deserve to be the head of the Hu family.

324
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:02,720
Sigh.

325
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,240
Right.

326
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,200
Since things have come to this,

327
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,400
I might as well admit it.

328
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:09,330
I, Qiao Xin, don't need to pretend to be a man anymore.

329
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,720
You absolutely cannot admit it.

330
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,680
Do you hear me?

331
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:12,400
Hey.

332
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:14,120
She can actually hear me.

333
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:15,680
Fine.

334
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:17,520
Then I will tell you today.

335
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,880
You can't tell them.

336
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:20,880
Hey.

337
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,200
Child.

338
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,820
You must not say it.

339
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:26,480
Master.

340
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:30,160
Seeing those layers of white gauze around Long'er's chest,

341
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:31,800
my heart aches.

342
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,280
Yun'er is dead,

343
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,840
and you can no longer have children.

344
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:36,500
If I don't sacrifice Long'er,

345
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,840
how can we protect the Hu family business?

346
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:39,680
If the Hu family

347
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:42,560
falls into the hands of a villain like Hu Wenyi,

348
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:45,760
it will be doomed forever.

349
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,240
I, Hu Linglong,

350
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,800
am indeed a woman.
